{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775883624820,"sessionID":"ses_285169c88ffe90hQDn8Kg9pqnS","part":{"id":"prt_d7ae99eb8001M0MYYuDk79F8NX","messageID":"msg_d7ae981df001MFHZmvDX41FGYf","sessionID":"ses_285169c88ffe90hQDn8Kg9pqnS","type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"toolu_tool-421e3ee00b9d40d692407e89fdbf6c0d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"include":"*.md","pattern":"AR-032|Dockerfile.*multi|多阶段构建"},"output":"Found 30 matches\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-032: Dockerfile Multi-Stage Build - Implementation Summary\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/README.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) Tasks\n  Line 975: - Base design document: `changes/AR-032/design.md`\n  Line 976: - Base specification document: `changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md`\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/design.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 — Design Document\n  Line 9: **Source Root:** `/changes/AR-032/`\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) Delta Specification\n  Line 4: - **AR ID**: AR-032\n  Line 5: - **Title**: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n  Line 13: This delta specification provides comprehensive acceptance criteria for Dockerfile multi-stage builds with 3 images in the AgentCube project. It defines requirements for building AgentCube components using multi-stage Docker builds to optimize image size, build time, and security. The specification covers three distinct stages: builder, dependency, and runtime stages, with detailed GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios to ensure proper implementation of the multi-stage build pattern.\n  Line 19: The system SHALL implement Dockerfile multi-stage builds with three distinct stages: builder, dependency, and runtime.\n  Line 358: This delta specification defines multi-stage Dockerfile builds for the AgentCube project. The multi-stage builds are an optimization over existing single-stage builds and produce the same runtime images with improved efficiency and security. The final runtime images maintain compatibility with existing deployments, as they contain the same binaries and dependencies.\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n  Line 9: 实现高效的 Dockerfile 多阶段构建策略，达到以下目标：\n  Line 11: - **镜像体积优化** - 通过多阶段构建移除构建工具、源代码和临时文件，显著减小最终镜像体积\n  Line 34: 1. **多阶段构建架构**\n  Line 111: - **Docker 20.10+**: 多阶段构建支持\n  Line 270: **选择**: 不采纳 - 多阶段构建的体积和安全性优势显著\n  Line 336: **选择**: 不采纳 - 多阶段构建在 Dockerfile 内部更简洁和自包含\n  Line 676:    - 使用多阶段构建\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/spec.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-032 Specification: Dockerfile 多阶段构建\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/CHANGE.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n  Line 4: - **AR**: AR-032\n  Line 5: - **Title**: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/tasks.md:\n  Line 478: - AR-032: Workload Manager Deployment (depends on RBAC configuration)\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md:\n  Line 371: - [ ] Define Dockerfile content as multi-line string\n  Line 389: - [ ] Define Dockerfile content as multi-line string\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-020/proposal.md:\n  Line 66:    - 优化的多阶段构建\n  Line 179: - 多阶段构建减少镜像大小","metadata":{"matches":30,"truncated":false},"title":"AR-032|Dockerfile.*multi|多阶段构建","time":{"start":1775883624797,"end":1775883624818}}}}
