Criteria**:\n914: - Build context size is reasonable (< 100 MB)\n915: - Unnecessary files are excluded\n916: - .dockerignore is effective\n917: - Build context size is documented\n918: \n919: ---\n920: \n921: ### Task 45: Final integration test\n922: - [ ] Perform complete build pipeline\n923: - [ ] Build all three image variants\n924: - [ ] Run all three images\n925: - [ ] Verify all functionality works\n926: - [ ] Run all tests\n927: - [ ] Verify no errors\n928: - [ ] Document results\n929: \n930: **Verification**:\n931: ```bash\n932: docker build -t agentcube:latest .\n933: docker build --target builder -t agentcube:dev .\n934: docker build --target verifier -t agentcube:test .\n935: docker images | grep agentcube\n936: ```\n937: \n938: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n939: - All three variants build successfully\n940: - All images run correctly\n941: - All tests pass\n942: - No errors in build or runtime\n943: - Integration test results are documented\n944: \n945: ---\n946: \n947: ## Summary\n948: \n949: **Total Tasks**: 45\n950: **Estimated Effort**: S (Small) - 8-12 hours\n951: \n952: ### Key Deliverables\n953: 1. **Multi-stage Dockerfile** with 3 stages (builder, verifier, runtime)\n954: 2. **.dockerignore** file for build context optimization\n955: 3. **Build scripts** for automated builds\n956: 4. **Documentation** (docs/docker.md, README.md updates)\n957: 5. **Testing validation** (unit, integration, security tests)\n958: \n959: ### Success Criteria\n960: - All three Dockerfile stages are implemented correctly\n961: - Multi-stage build produces minimal runtime image (< 250 MB)\n962: - Production image size is at least 50% smaller than builder image\n963: - Non-root user is configured correctly\n964: - Build tools are excluded from production image\n965: - Health checks are configured and working\n966: - All tests pass\n967: - No critical security vulnerabilities\n968: - Multi-architecture builds work correctly\n969: - Documentation is complete\n970: \n971: ### Dependencies\n972: - Docker 20.10+ (for multi-stage build support)\n973: - Go 1.21+ (for building AgentCube components)\n974: - Python 3.11+ (for picod component)\n975: - Base design document: `changes/AR-032/design.md`\n976: - Base specification document: `changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md`\n977: \n978: ### Blocked By\n979: - None (design stage ST-3 completed)\n980: \n981: ### Blocks\n982: - AR-033: Controller Manager Deployment (depends on Docker images)\n983: - AR-034: Workload Manager Deployment (depends on Docker images)\n984: - AR-035: Router Deployment (depends on Docker images)\n985: \n986: ### Notes\n987: - Multi-stage builds are critical for security and image size optimization\n988: - Always use specific image versions, never `latest` tag\n989: - Follow Dockerfile best practices for layer optimization\n990: - Run security scans before deploying to production\n991: - Use buildx for multi-architecture builds\n992: - Document any exceptions to security best practices\n\n(End of file - total 992 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) Tasks\n\n**Module**: `docker`\n**Language**: Dockerfile\n**Size**: S\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Create .dockerignore file\n- [ ] Create .dockerignore file in project root\n- [ ] Add .git directory to exclude\n- [ ] Add *.md files to exclude (README.md, docs/)\n- [ ] Add test files (*_test.go, pytest.ini, .coverage)\n- [ ] Add development files (.vscode/, .idea/, *.swp)\n- [ ] Add build artifacts (dist/, build/, *.exe)\n- [ ] Add CI/CD files (.github/, .gitlab-ci.yml)\n- [ ] Add OS files (.DS_Store, Thumbs.db)\n- [ ] Add temporary files (tmp/, temp/, *.tmp)\n- [ ] Add .dockerignore itself to exclude","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775883629453,"end":1775883629470}}}}
